<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从藏有宝藏的洞穴回来以后，阿拉丁改变了许多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他觉得自己不再是孩子了，他不想整天都在街上玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他感觉自己长大了，也想帮助妈妈了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁看了看用来装食物的盘子，想到了一个主意：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要拿一个盘子到集市去卖掉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是个不错的盘子，但是可能不是真的金子。”泽巴说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可能只能换来几个铜钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁把盘子包在外套里，去了集市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他找到一间古董店，里面摆满了碗、盘，还有杯子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把盘子卖给你的话，你出多少钱买？”阿拉丁问商人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老人拿过来盘子仔细看了看。“纯金。”他自言自语道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他抬起头看了看阿拉丁，心想：“但是这个男孩儿好像不知道这是金子做的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他狡猾地对阿拉丁说：“是个不错的盘子，你想卖多少钱？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它值多少钱？”阿拉丁问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老人笑了笑，从口袋拿出来一个金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀，谢谢您，先生！”阿拉丁高兴地喊道。他拿走了金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是商人马上就后悔了。“说不定给两个铜钱就够了呢。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那以后，每次当阿拉丁需要钱时，他就把盘子拿去卖给商人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每次，那个老人都嘟囔着付给阿拉丁一个金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，阿拉丁把最后一个盘子包在外套里，朝商店走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走着走着，另一个商店的商人走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子，我看见你经过很多次了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你总是去那个老商人那里。给我看看你卖的什么，说不定我能付更多的钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我已经卖到了一个好价钱。”阿拉丁骄傲地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>新商人拿过阿拉丁的盘子，称了重量。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你卖给那个老人的都是这种盘子吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”阿拉丁回答道，“一模一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他给你多少钱？”新商人问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个金币！”阿拉丁咧开嘴笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他骗了你。”商人说，“这个盘子是纯金的，它值一百个金币！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真是个傻瓜。”阿拉丁红着脸低声说，“那个老头一定一直在笑话我呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，但是你可以从中得到教训。”新商人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那天起，阿拉丁每天都去集市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和每一个商人聊天，并从中学习经商。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他问了很多问题，知道了很多东西的价值。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁有时候去一个卖钻石和宝石的商人那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他倾听那个商人讲的所有的话，看他买东西和卖东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也就是这个时候，他知道了他的玻璃水果根本不是玻璃，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而是世界上最珍贵的，甚至连国王都不曾拥有的稀有宝石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天早上，阿拉丁像往常一样去了集市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他到那里时，发现国王的一个手下正骑着马对着人群说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“全体市民！”他大喊，“锁上你们的商店，然后回家！违令者格杀勿论！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>